{"id": "ChIJezlQP-PHwoARkgEoj56TXEg", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 316, "displayName": {"text": "STAGGER COFFEE", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJezlQP-PHwoARkgEoj56TXEg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OM1psY3dSbkV5Vm04M1kxVnZZVTVNU205aFdYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I got the Jasmine matcha for $7 and it is so yummy!!! The barista warned it’s on the sweeter side and offered to do half sweet, but I wanted to try it as is. It is pretty sweet but still very flavorful and delicious. I’m dying to try their coconut matcha and double hojicha so maybe next time I’ll splurge and get two drinks!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I got the Jasmine matcha for $7 and it is so yummy!!! The barista warned it’s on the sweeter side and offered to do half sweet, but I wanted to try it as is. It is pretty sweet but still very flavorful and delicious. I’m dying to try their coconut matcha and double hojicha so maybe next time I’ll splurge and get two drinks!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Gabrielle Urman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110759022429052469822/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKD9x5QSeiQM6MGeSDaI6ZIxMvMSqcbh0qxOlu6A1ftI2fAWtGx=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-01T05:20:41.824002705Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OM1psY3dSbkV5Vm04M1kxVnZZVTVNU205aFdYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OM1psY3dSbkV5Vm04M1kxVnZZVTVNU205aFdYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7e33f50397b:0x485c939e8f280192"}, {"name": "places/ChIJezlQP-PHwoARkgEoj56TXEg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GbVFrcFdaMXBaYnpGR2FuaFlXVlZhUms1SldIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "1. The drink was delicious and well-crafted! I really like the matcha creamtop!\n2. The spot has chill casual vibes! The interior has high ceilings!\n3. The staff was friendly and timely with my order! It was ready after 5 mins!\nNote: This spot does have individual restroom for customers!\n\nPhoto: Double Matcha", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "1. The drink was delicious and well-crafted! I really like the matcha creamtop!\n2. The spot has chill casual vibes! The interior has high ceilings!\n3. The staff was friendly and timely with my order! It was ready after 5 mins!\nNote: This spot does have individual restroom for customers!\n\nPhoto: Double Matcha", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Andy Vu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107058405522234792971/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM7eqOVi2qqP-FLPL_I7l01i_UC0CeUJw0mmnuNh8j2WNuFGYK=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-16T16:33:52.450895949Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GbVFrcFdaMXBaYnpGR2FuaFlXVlZhUms1SldIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GbVFrcFdaMXBaYnpGR2FuaFlXVlZhUms1SldIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7e33f50397b:0x485c939e8f280192"}, {"name": "places/ChIJezlQP-PHwoARkgEoj56TXEg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SclN5MHhWQzFuVm1Wb1YySjNabVZrVG5OR1ExRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Matcha is 10/10 and the service is amazing. My wife was iffy about getting a double matcha with vanilla and when they gave her the drink they told her if she doesn’t like it they can remake it. she tried it and wasn’t a big fan so they offered to remake her a new drink. Offered to pay them but they said it’s ok and even let us keep the first drink which I drank (I don’t really like matcha and it was really good).\n\n10/10 service don’t see customer service like this anymore. Definitely spend your money here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Matcha is 10/10 and the service is amazing. My wife was iffy about getting a double matcha with vanilla and when they gave her the drink they told her if she doesn’t like it they can remake it. she tried it and wasn’t a big fan so they offered to remake her a new drink. Offered to pay them but they said it’s ok and even let us keep the first drink which I drank (I don’t really like matcha and it was really good).\n\n10/10 service don’t see customer service like this anymore. Definitely spend your money here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "aryan a", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117698920253951609063/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMpKaCqUIMNliTGgm8uBmT9-WkP0LgjHnGyf7Xe6jfpf_ZvPQ57Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T23:21:09.480776329Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SclN5MHhWQzFuVm1Wb1YySjNabVZrVG5OR1ExRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SclN5MHhWQzFuVm1Wb1YySjNabVZrVG5OR1ExRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7e33f50397b:0x485c939e8f280192"}, {"name": "places/ChIJezlQP-PHwoARkgEoj56TXEg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT204MmRqWkZUamx4WVZNM09FNTNlSFU0UTJoQlprRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "One of the best matchas I ever had! I usually don’t like too sweet matchas but this was just the perfect amount of sweetness. We got the double matcha it was so creamy and perfect, never seen anywhere else does matcha like this one. It I had more days in LA, I’d definitely stop by again", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "One of the best matchas I ever had! I usually don’t like too sweet matchas but this was just the perfect amount of sweetness. We got the double matcha it was so creamy and perfect, never seen anywhere else does matcha like this one. It I had more days in LA, I’d definitely stop by again", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Dilara Etush", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115029210724436032518/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPBhsHu6B6RGv2Z5YN1qP4ml1vlZiPwBoRCpfnZPzK_Hekbg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-07T16:27:12.293183509Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT204MmRqWkZUamx4WVZNM09FNTNlSFU0UTJoQlprRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT204MmRqWkZUamx4WVZNM09FNTNlSFU0UTJoQlprRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7e33f50397b:0x485c939e8f280192"}, {"name": "places/ChIJezlQP-PHwoARkgEoj56TXEg/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poc2RrVkdaRVpqWXprMk1URnhXVU5oVEZBeE1tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I got the jasmine matcha and my husband got the double matcha.  The jasmine matcha is on the sweeter side, so imo if there was 1 more gram of matcha it would taste a little more balanced.  I would still drink the jasmine matcha again though, probably half sweet if that’s an option. The double matcha is yummy and has a great texture as always.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I got the jasmine matcha and my husband got the double matcha.  The jasmine matcha is on the sweeter side, so imo if there was 1 more gram of matcha it would taste a little more balanced.  I would still drink the jasmine matcha again though, probably half sweet if that’s an option. The double matcha is yummy and has a great texture as always.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mugheesah Alidina", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101840411759622539697/reviews", "photoUri": "h